  <name>HardInfo</name>
  <summary>System profiler and benchmark</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
    HardInfo is a system profiler and benchmark for Linux systems. It is able to obtain information from both hardware and basic software, and organize them in a simple to use GUI.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Report generation (in either HTML or plain text)</li>
      <li>Benchmark result synchronization</li>
      <li>Ability to explore the information on remote computers</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
